WEBVTT

2
00:00:03.078 --> 00:00:09.077
Nau mai ki tēnei whakaaturanga ipurangi o te tēpu ko Chris Winitana ahau.

3
00:00:09.077 --> 00:00:25.009
Ko wō tātou reo wā tātou whakatangitangi, ko ā tātou tikanga tonu mō tēnei mea o te waiata, nā wēnei taonga katoa te Māori me ā tātou tikanga me tō tātou reo rangatira i tāre.

4
00:00:25.009 --> 00:00:32.085
Kei konei wāku rangatira hei whakautu i ēnei pātai e hāngai ana ki te ao waiata Māori, reo Māori.

5
00:00:32.085 --> 00:00:33.088
Tēnā ngā hiwi.

6
00:00:33.088 --> 00:00:38.049
Kei te puta mai he hunga, he matatau ki te reo, he rangatahi,

7
00:00:38.049 --> 00:00:41.022
kei moumou me aha rātou,

8
00:00:41.022 --> 00:00:45.044
me whai i tā koro mā, ka kui mā te āhua o te hanganga o ngā waiata.

9
00:00:45.044 --> 00:00:49.005
Me whai rānei i ngā momo waiata o ēnei rā, he aha ō whakaaro?

10
00:00:49.005 --> 00:00:52.083
ki tāku titiro me whakarite,

11
00:00:52.083 --> 00:00:57.046
me kī te ao Māori, me whakakotahi rānei te ao Māori me te ao Pākehā.

12
00:00:57.046 --> 00:01:00.067
Kia rite ai ki tā rātou noho.

13
00:01:00.067 --> 00:01:04.088
Mōku ake, ko ngā tamariki puta mai ana i ngā wharekura

14
00:01:04.088 --> 00:01:10.005
e matatau ana ki te reo Māori, e rua ngā momo waiata e arohaina ana e rātou,

15
00:01:10.005 --> 00:01:13.064
ko te kapa haka, ko ngā waiata a ngā mangumangu o ēnei rā.

16
00:01:13.064 --> 00:01:16.017
Nā ko tāku ki a rātou me whakakotahi,

17
00:01:16.017 --> 00:01:20.017
me whakakotahi ki ahau kia puta ai he tuakiri Māori ake,

18
00:01:20.017 --> 00:01:22.037
tēnā koe, tēnā koe.

19
00:01:22.037 --> 00:01:23.080
Whiri, ka mihi.

20
00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:28.081
roa kē koe e haere ana i tēnei huarahi he kaiwaiata koe,

21
00:01:28.081 --> 00:01:36.010
he aha tāu nā tohu nunui ki te rangatahi e whai atu ana i wō tapuwai?

22
00:01:36.010 --> 00:01:41.047
reo Māori tēnei kaiwaiata, he aha tō tino tohu ki a rātou?

23
00:01:41.047 --> 00:01:44.082
Kaua e wareware ki tō koutou reo māori,

24
00:01:44.082 --> 00:01:52.010
mehemea ka raruraru tirohia i roto i ngā waiata tawhito, ngā kupu a ngā tūpuna.

25
00:01:52.010 --> 00:01:57.024
Hei aha, hei kīnaki, hei kīnaki, hei āwhina i a koe,

26
00:01:57.024 --> 00:02:03.008
kia kaua koe e wareware i ahu mai koe mai hea.

27
00:02:03.008 --> 00:02:10.026
Koro napi, he kaiwhakangahau koe mai anō, he kaiwaiata, ka mutu he Māori,

28
00:02:10.026 --> 00:02:16.060
he aha tēnei mea te kaiwhakangahau Māori,

29
00:02:16.060 --> 00:02:25.058
ki wō whakaaro, he aha tana mahi, ki tāku ko te kaiwhakangahau, he whakamahi i tōna tinana me tōna mōhiotanga

30
00:02:25.058 --> 00:02:30.051
hei hiki i te iwi, hei whakamaria i te iwi,

31
00:02:30.051 --> 00:02:34.094
hei... hei tango i te riri, te pukuriri, ērā āhuatanga.

32
00:02:34.094 --> 00:02:38.056
ka whakakatakatangia e koe he rongoā tērā

33
00:02:38.056 --> 00:02:41.040
e... e tau ai te rangimāriatanga,

34
00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:48.031
kua kite au i ngā tāngata kua haere mai hei te pukuriri, engari ka haere mai ngā koroua

35
00:02:48.031 --> 00:02:55.005
tohunga ki tēnei mahi ki te whakangahau, hei reira e pakipaki ana, e hoa noho, e noho koe,

36
00:02:55.005 --> 00:02:58.096
anā kei reira ka timata ki te kani, ko...

37
00:02:58.096 --> 00:03:05.021
ko kī ētahi, ko pōrangi, ko kī ētahi, e hoa, e noho i roto i tērā

38
00:03:05.021 --> 00:03:08.091
kei te whakakotahi ia i ngā tāngata i a rātou e kō ana,

39
00:03:08.091 --> 00:03:11.014
ā te mutunga ka kanikani ka kata.

40
00:03:11.014 --> 00:03:15.095
Kua mutu te riri, kua mutu, kua pātai rātou, e riri ana tātou mō te aha?

41
00:03:15.095 --> 00:03:20.075
Nā wai te take i āio rātou, nā te kaiwhakangahau.

42
00:03:20.075 --> 00:03:22.033
Tēnā koe kōrua.

43
00:03:22.033 --> 00:03:24.059
Koutou ka mihi,

44
00:03:24.059 --> 00:03:27.085
tēnā ngā waiata Māori kei konei,

45
00:03:27.085 --> 00:03:32.042
kei te tēpu haurua o te 9, pō Wenerei, Whakaata Māori.

46
00:03:32.042 --> 00:03:41.077
Huri mai te taringa ki te whakarongo.
